994
01:26:43.778 --> 01:26:46.911
The vindictive gods
are now at hand.

995
01:26:52.556 --> 01:26:53.654
Look around!

996
01:26:54.789 --> 01:26:57.053
See your brothers and sisters!

997
01:26:57.522 --> 01:26:59.461
And view our numbers.

998
