Lay into them. Wipe them out!

1022
01:29:47.456 --> 01:29:50.534
Ask your daughters
for help, Boudica. Now!

1023
01:29:52.637 --> 01:29:54.229
Girls!

1024
01:29:54.230 --> 01:29:55.835
Are you going to help us?

1025
01:29:55.836 --> 01:29:58.333
The time for fighting
is over, Mother.

1026
01:29:59.138 --> 01:30:01.137
Then what?

1027
01:30:01.138 --> 01:30:02.810
It's time for you to join us.

1028
01:30:06.079 --> 01:30:07.276
