1030
01:30:18.487 --> 01:30:20.255
I go where you go.

1031
01:30:20.256 --> 01:30:21.664
On my command.

1032
01:30:24.801 --> 01:30:26.030
On your word, my queen.

1033
01:30:26.031 --> 01:30:28.704
Let's go.

